Package: quicklm
Title: Quick checks and visualizations for linear models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Hasbany",
           family = "James",
           role = c("aut"),
    person(given = "Bodwin",
           family = "Kelly",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kelly@bodwin.us"))
Description: Simple functions for checking and visualizing 
linear model assumptions. Allows the user to simlutaneously test many variables for 
model inclusion, and provides simple and clear output.  Plots residuals against
many variables, and checks normality.
